shall maintain free from leaks, obstructions and other defects, all occupant owned and installed
equipment including, but not limited to:
(1) Dishwashers;
(2) Clothes washing machines and dryers;
(3) Garbage grinders;
(4) Air conditioners;
(5) Microwave ovens;
